LongGammaWrapperClose
├── when the stored user calls close on an open position
│   ├── it voluntarily burns the long via dispatch with size zero and false and zero builder code
│   ├── it drives numberOfLegs of the wrapper to zero
│   └── it transitions state from Open to Closed
├── when a non user address calls close
│   └── it reverts NotUser
└── when close is called while not Open
    └── it reverts WrongState
